      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_1_4_4\">Desktop virtualization software <span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"1_4\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li> </label>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_1_4_4\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMarket offers a number of easy, affordable, all-in-one software appliances enabling desktop\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIT to rapidly deliver centrally-managed virtual desktops for less than the cost of new PCs. <br>References\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- <a href=\"http://www.vmware.com/uk/smb/desktop-virtualization\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.vmware.com\">VMWare</a>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\tvirtualizaed and remote desktops solutions. <br> <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"https://www.citrix.com/products/vdi-in-a-box/overview.html\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.citrix.com\">Citrix\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>scalable, affordable VDI for businesses of any size.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t<div class=\"form-radio-buttons\" id=\"V2\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t<label> <span>2. Energy performance improvement and monitoring </span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_1\">Use energy monitoring and management hardware and\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsoftware <span class=\"checkmark\" id=\"2_1\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTo understand how to change something, it is essential to assess it first. List of energy\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmanagement software for organization may vary from open source to commercial fully\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsupported products. <br>Reference - <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"http://www.capterra.com/energy-management-software/\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.capterra.com\">Energy\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmanagement software</a>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_2\">Thin clients deployment <span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"2_2\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_2\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThink of purchasing low power CPU's and implementing thin clients.<br> <b>Thin\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclient computing</b> provides users with the same interface, applications, and performance as a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdesktop based computer but through a slim lined desktop device. Because the thin client's\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tperformance is driven by a server instead of a local processor, there can be significant\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpower savings when used in a large environment. But thin clients are not always an\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tappropriate solution - although they lead to cheaper clients with less energy consumption,\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthey also lead to more communications and data centre applications and potentially higher\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tenergy consumption in the data centre. This balance needs to be assessed for your own\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tparticular circumstance.<BR> <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"http://greenict.org.uk/sites/default/files/Green%20ICT%20Handbook.pdf\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.greenict.org.uk\">Reference</a>.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_2_1\">Switch off unused devices completely <span\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_2\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_2_1\">Shut down PC equipment after hours, or use remote\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmonitoring software solutions to do so.</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\">Turn off peripherals, or set them to stand-by mode respectively <span\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_2\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\">Switch on/off WiFi Access Points <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_2\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_2_2\">Power management software can automate switch off\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tactivities <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_3\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_2_2\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou can set up a 'dimming and switch off' option on your PC by adjusting OS settings.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDimming and switching off occurs automatically after a certain period (e.g. 5 minutes) when\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe PC has been idle. You can start saving energy by looking for the power options in your\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tOS. Computers and monitors account for half the electricity used in an office and energy is\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbeing wasted every day, even by \"energy saving\" hardware. For example, in a company with 200\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPCs, turning off all the computers and monitors every night and at weekends would save\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&pound;12,000 a year.<br> <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"http://greenict.org.uk/sites/default/files/Green%20ICT%20Handbook.pdf\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.greenict.org.uk\">Reference</a>.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_4\">Integration assessment into management system (Green IT\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tofficer) <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_4\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_4\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCarbon emissions can be calculated from the energy consumption of your ICT department's\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tinfrastructure, which is then useful in planning and prioritising projects.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Step 1 - Establish a measurement team. Creating a team to measure the carbon\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfootprint is important. Asking each team member to carry out the measurement activity\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\trelevant to their responsibilities is key to measure correctly and to spark sustainable\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthinking.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Step 2 - Define a measurement timeline. It sounds basic, but putting a timeline in\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tplace will ensure that this activity, which may not be viewed as business critical, is\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcompleted in a timely fashion.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Step 3 - Undertake and collate measurement activities. The <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"./Calculate.jsp\">CALCULATE</a> section shows and explains how to make estimations on\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thow to convert energy consumption of ICT equipment into a carbon footprint.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://greenict.org.uk/sites/default/files/Green%20ICT%20Handbook.pdf\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.greenict.org.uk\">Reference</a>.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_4_1\">Use multifunction devices<span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"2_4\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_4_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tConsolidate equipment and use multifunction devices (printers, copiers, scanners).Sometimes\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcopiers are on stand-by day and night in offices. Small copiers consume about 50 watts and\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlarge copiers about 100 watts on standby power in sleep mode. Modern photocopiers are often\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpacked with features that minimize energy consumption in idle mode. On older machines you\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcan save energy with a timer. That clock switches the equipment off during the hours that no\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tone is present. You save 10 to 20% on energy (cost).<br> <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"http://carbonfootprintmanagement.com/\"\n");
