      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t<label> <span>5. Waste management </span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_5_1\">Adopt policies for ICT equipment recycling, recovery,\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\treuse of materials and responsible disposal <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"5_1\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_5_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe WEEE (Waste Electrical and Electronic Equipment) directive means that the disposal of\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\telectronic equipment is no longer the responsibility of the user organisation. The\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tresponsibility falls to the manufacturers and sellers who should pay for the collection of\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tequipment when it has reached end of life and either recycle or responsibly dispose of it.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tRemember, when buying new equipment - ensure you are given the details of who to contact\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twhen you no longer require the equipment to arrange collection.<br> <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"http://greenict.org.uk/sites/default/files/Green%20ICT%20Handbook.pdf\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.greenict.org.uk\">Reference</a>.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_5_1_1\">Extending ICT equipment life - waste prevention <span\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"checkmark\" name=\"5_1\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_5_1_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBy simply extending the refresh cycle of PCs in your organisation you reduce your\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\torganisation's environmental impact. Some manufacturers are now making efforts to find out\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe level of embedded carbon that is in their equipment, but it is not an easy task because\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tICT equipment is made of many components that are sourced from many different suppliers.<br>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://greenict.org.uk/sites/default/files/Green%20ICT%20Handbook.pdf\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonClick=\"return confirm('The link will be opened in a new tab..')\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"www.greenict.org.uk\">Reference</a>.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_5_2\">General Recycling <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"5_2\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_5_2\">Start from simple wastes separation in your office\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thousehold and find contractors to collect them for recycling.</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_5_2_1\">Recycle used electronic devices<span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"5_2\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_5_2_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThere are many electronics recycling organisations which will recycle or reuse unwanted\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tequipment where possible, in accordance with the WEEE directive, the Environmental\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tProtection Act and the Data Protection Act. Also, look at how consumables can be reused or\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\trecycled. For example, talk to your printer cartridge supplier about arranging regular\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcollection of used cartridges for refill and reuse.<br> <a\n");
